replies.body:
Yo these new icons are dope though right?!
{{sticker:sg-ezreal}} 

Back to the task at hand. You might be able to get a bit of a better signal by adjusting some of those hotspot settings like DNS servers and such following the [**connection guide**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752664-Troubleshooting-Connection-Issues), but overall you may not be able to get much better signal since you're running on a hotspot =\ . Those work by essentially turning your phone into a router, which diminishes the signal a bit more on top of the fact that your phone hardware just isn't built to function as a gaming router.
